      <title>日本央行缺乏债券购买削减细节导致日元脆弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行要求投资者等到 7 月份会议才能公布缩减债券购买规模的具体细节，这导致日元可能进一步下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:31:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪拜环球港务集团计划到 2029 年向非洲港口投资 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/dp-world-plans-3-billion-investment-in-african-ports-by-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜环球港务集团计划在未来三到五年内投资 30 亿美元在非洲建设新的港口和物流基础设施，以满足包括对关键矿产出口的激增的需求在内的长期增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/dp-world-plans-3-billion-investment-in-african-ports-by-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 14:45:06 GMT</pubDate>
